The paper deals with a variant of propositional logic that is related to data analysis and machine learning, specifically the concept of association rules. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.IT (Information Theory).
